dct_alternative_sm: Map of Amoy and surrounding region which includes Heng-Hoa, Chin-Chew, Chang-Chew, Eng-Chhun, Lung-Yen, and the district around each
dct_description_sm: by Rev. L. W. Kip, D.D.
Bar scales in "(Mandarin Leagues)," "(Long or Country Leagues)," and "(English Miles)."
In transliterated Min Chinese, with English translations.
Shows cities, capitals, roads and paths, bridges, passes, market days, postal agencies, drainage.
